Institute Web and Mobile Operations Team 201617

Hello all,

Here is the call for coordinators for Institute WebOps/MobOps team.

Anyone who has interest in web hosting, designing websites, building chrome
extensions or hybrid mobile and desktop applications may apply for the
post. This is open only for B.Tech/Dual Degree second years. The
selection will be based on an interview during which an assignment will be
given. Based on which, one might get selected into the team.

Who are we?

In the past the institute Web Operations team has been taking care of
entire student related web operations such as students portal, mess
registration
and has assisted Hostels, CFI, IBOT, techsoc, Sports, NSS, EML etc. in setting
up and running their websites. We have brought about many new initiatives
this year, which will further our cause to ease student life in insti and
also help organize information over time. Some of our many new initiatives
include IITM Video Conference app
, Information
Portal , Insti Maps
 , Course Review
 , Research Portal
 and many other backend
features to bring about a centralization among the sites. We have been
developed a mobile app for integrated use of all these sites, as well as
browser extensions to make them more accessible. You can find it here
<&hlen .
The coming year a number of projects like " Notifications portal, Students
Library , HAS Portal , Buy and Sell " etc. are being brought. We are mainly
looking forward to standardize and build upon the existing sites, hoping
that they be more useful for each students in our institute. There is
definitely a lot of exciting work waiting to be done!


Eligibility Criterion:

    Minimum CGPA of 7 with no "U" or "W" or "I" in the grade card as on
   today.
    Successful completion of NCC/NSO/NSS.
    No history of punishment by the academic and the hostel disciplinary
   committee.

Incentives Offered:

    Chance to implement your own ideas in the institute and to get
them certified
   as an internship.
    Tshirts and Treats.
    Recommendation to Web based start ups and core/coordinator positions
   of other web operations team operating in the Institute.

Deadline for the application of the post is 11:59pm, 07082016.

Please fill the form to apply for the post:
Institute WebOps/MobOps  Call for Coordinators


The details of the interview will be mailed to the candidates on
09082016.

P.S :  We also have two positions open for super coordinator open for 3rd
years and above . If interested fill this form

 before 11:59pm, 07082016.

Regards,
Institute WebOps/MobOps.

